```

**Why**: Reduces latency from ~200ms (Europe) to ~30-50ms (local).

---

#### 4. **Low-Data Mode Template Variant** (Auto-Detect)
```typescript
// hooks/use-connection-quality.ts
export function useConnectionQuality() {
  const [connectionType, setConnectionType] = useState<'4g' | '3g' | '2g'>('4g');

  useEffect(() => {
    if ('connection' in navigator) {
      const conn = (navigator as any).connection;
      setConnectionType(conn.effectiveType || '4g');
    }
  }, []);

  return connectionType;
}

// In template renderer
const connectionType = useConnectionQuality();
const templateVariant = connectionType === '2g' || connectionType === '3g' 
  ? 'low-data'  // Stripped-down version (no custom fonts, compressed images)
  : 'full';     // Full template with animations
```

**Low-data variant**:
- No custom fonts (system fonts only)
- Images compressed to 50% quality
- No background images
- Simplified layout (no CSS grid/flexbox complexity)

---

#### 5. **Template Preview Optimization** (Marketplace)
```typescript
