  return (
    <div>
      {/* THUMBNAIL (pre-rendered, <20KB) */}
      <img 
        src={`/template-previews/${template.id}-thumb.webp`} 
        loading="lazy"
        alt={template.name}
      />

      {/* LIVE PREVIEW (only on click) */}
      {isSelected && (
        <iframe 
          src={`/pro/preview/${template.id}?low-data=true`}
          loading="lazy"
        />
      )}
    </div>
  );
}
```

**Strategy**: 
- Marketplace shows **static thumbnails** (not live renders)
- Live preview loads **only on click**
- Preview uses **low-data mode** by default

