|--------|-------------|-------------|----------------|
| **First Contentful Paint** | <1.5s | <0.8s | Critical CSS inlined, SSR |
| **Time to Interactive** | <3s | <1.5s | No template JS, lazy images |
| **Total Page Weight** | <500KB | <1MB | Compressed images, 2 fonts max |
| **Template Switch Time** | <200ms | <50ms | CSS variables (no re-render) |

